songs.lyrics:
Opening verse starts here
The rhythm picks up in line two
Line three builds the energy
Line four leads to the chorus

songs.title: From the Inside
songs.lyrics:
Verse one begins with power
Second line adds emotion
Third line raises intensity
Fourth line sets up the hook

songs.title: Let Me Free
songs.lyrics:
Starting with a gentle intro
Building up the story here
Third line adds more depth
Fourth line completes the thought

songs.title: Must Have Been Love
songs.lyrics:
Emotional opening line here
Second line continues the feeling
Third line deepens the message
Fourth line brings it together

songs.lyrics:
Original composition starts
Second line sets the mood
Third line creates atmosphere
Fourth line completes verse one

songs.title: Living On a Prayer
songs.lyrics:
Classic rock anthem begins
Second line pumps up energy
Third line drives forward
Fourth line sets up the chorus

songs.title: Slipping in my car
songs.lyrics:
Driving through the night alone
Windows down, the radio on
Feeling like I'm losing control
Slipping in my car, body and soul

songs.title: Rolling on a river
songs.lyrics:
Left a good job in the city
Working for the man every night and day
And I never lost one minute of sleeping
Worrying 'bout the way things might have been

songs.title: Lost
songs.lyrics:
Wandering through empty streets
Searching for what I can't find
Every turn leads nowhere
Lost in space and time

songs.title: Alone
songs.lyrics:
I hear the ticking of the clock
I'm lying here the room's pitch dark
I wonder where you are tonight
No answer on the telephone

songs.title: Holding Out for a Hero
songs.lyrics:
Where have all the good men gone
And where are all the gods?
Where's the streetwise Hercules
To fight the rising odds?

songs.title: Man I Feel like a woman
songs.lyrics:
Let's go girls, come on
I'm going out tonight, I'm feelin' alright
Gonna let it all hang out
Wanna make some noise, really raise my voice

songs.title: Billy Jean
songs.lyrics:
She was more like a beauty queen
From a movie scene
I said don't mind, but what do you mean
I am the one

songs.title: Heart of Glass
songs.lyrics:
Once I had a love and it was a gas
Soon turned out had a heart of glass
Seemed like the real thing only to find
Mucho mistrust, love's gone behind

songs.title: It's my life
songs.lyrics:
This ain't a song for the broken-hearted
No silent prayer for faith-departed
I ain't gonna be just a face in the crowd
You're gonna hear my voice when I shout it out loud

songs.title: Come together
songs.lyrics:
Here come old flat top
He come groovin' up slowly
He got joo joo eyeball
He one holy roller

songs.title: Flowers
songs.lyrics:
We were good, we were gold
Kinda dream that can't be sold
We were right 'til we weren't
Built a home and watched it burn

songs.title: Highway to hell
songs.lyrics:
Living easy, living free
Season ticket on a one way ride
Asking nothing, leave me be
Taking everything in my stride
